(3, 349.99, 'Nintendo Switch™ - OLED Model', 'Get the gaming system that lets you play the games you want, wherever you are, however you like. Bring the full home gaming system experience with you to the park, on an airplane, in a car, or to a friend''s apartment.', 310),
(3, 359.99, 'Nintendo Switch™', 'At home, Nintendo Switch™ rests in the Nintendo Switch Dock that connects the system to the TV and lets you play with family and friends in the comfort of your living room. By simply lifting Nintendo Switch from the dock, the system will instantly transition to portable mode, and the same great gaming experience that was being enjoyed at home now travels with you. The portability of Nintendo Switch is enhanced by its bright high-definition display. It brings the full home gaming system experience with you to the park, on an airplane, in a car, or to a friend’s apartment.', 193),
(3, 199.99, 'Nintendo Switch™ Lite', 'The Nintendo Switch Lite system is a small and light system at a great price. With a built-in +Control Pad, and a sleek unibody design, this system is great for on-the-go gaming and comes in a variety of colors.', 230),
(3, 79.99, 'Joy-Con™ (L)/(R)', 'One controller or two, vertifcal or sideways, motion controls or buttons...Joy-Con and Nintendo Switch™ give you total gameplay flexibility. Comes in a variety of colors.', 238),
(3, 69.99, 'Nintendo Switch Pro Controller', 'Take your game ssessions up a notch with the Pro Controller for Nintendo Switch™. Includes motion controls, HD rumble, build-in amiibo™ functionality, and more.', 230),
(3, 59.99, 'Animal Crossing™: New Horizons', 'Escape to a deserted island and create your own paradise as you explore, create and customize in teh Animal Crossing: New Horizons game. Your island getaway has a wealth of natural resources that can be used to craft everything from tools to creature comforts. You can hunt down insects at the crack of dawn, decorate your paradise throughout the day, or enjoy sunset on the beach while fishing in the ocean. The time of day and season match real life, so each day on your island is a chance to check in and find new surprises all year round.', 23),
(3, 24.99, 'Animal Crossing™: New Horizons - Happy Home Paradise', 'Join Lottie''s Paradise Planning team and travel to a distant archepelagio. This time, you are in charge of inviting characters as clients and helping them to live their own dream vacations. Choose from a variety of islands, with different terrain and climates and find one that matches your client''s vision. Then start desigining and start making their vacation dreams come true. Just wait until you see the look on your clients'' faces after you reveal the vacation home decorated just for them...', 34),
(3, 69.99, 'The Legend of Zelda™: Tears of the Kingdom', 'An epic adventure awaits in the Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom. In this sequel to the Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild game, you''ll decide your own path through the sprawling landscapes of Hyrule and the mysterious islands floating in the vast skies above. Can you harness the power of Link''s new abilities to fight back against the malevolent forces that threaten the kingdom?', 49),
(3, 59.99, 'The Legend of Zelda™: Breath of the Wild', 'Step into a world of discovery, exploration, and adventure in a boundary-breaking new game. Travel across vast fields, through forests, and to mountain peaks as you discover what has become of the kingdom of Hyrule in this stunning Open-Air Adventure.', 120),
(3, 6.24, 'Overcooked! 2', 'Overcooked returns with a brand-new helping of chaotic cooking action! Journey back to the Onion Kingdom and assemble your team of chefs in classic couch co-op or online play for up to four players. Hold onto your aprons... it''s time to save the world (again)', 13),
(3, 59.99, 'Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate', 'Gaming icons clash in the ultimate brawl you can play anytime, anywhere! Smash rivals off the stage as new characters Simon Belmont and King K. Roll join Inkling, Ridley, and every fighter in Super Smash Bros. history. Enjoy enhanced speed and combat at new stages based on the Castlevania series, Super Mario Odyssey, and more!', 42),
(3, 24.99, 'Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate: Fighters Pass', 'Expand your roster of fighters! Purchase the Fighters Pass now to get access to five additional playable fighters, five stages, and additional music. Announced fighters include Joker, the Hero, Banjo &Kazooie, Terry Bogard, and Byleth!', 48),
(3, 24.99, 'Super Smash Bros.™ ultimate: Fighter Pass Vol. 2', 'Expand your roster of fighters! Purchase the Fighters Pass now to get access to six additional playable fighters, plus additional stages, and music as they release. Announced fighters include Min Min, Steve & Alex, Sephiroth, Pyra/Mythra, Kazuya, and Sora!', 42),
(3, 4.99, 'Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate: Piranha Plant Standalone Fighter', 'Piranha Plant joins the battle as a stand-aline fighter! With its powerful bite, Poison Breath, and ability to call in Petey Piranha for a larger-than-life Final Smash, this fighter''s ferocity is as sharp as its teeth. Ready your pipes and flowerpods; your opponent won''t see you coming! (Then again, Piranha Plant doesn''t really "see" either. It doesn''t have eyes.)', 23),
(3, 55.99, 'Splatoon™ 2', 'The Inklings are back to splat more ink and claim more turf in this colorful and chaotic 4-on-4 action shooter. For the first time, take Turf War battles on-the-go with the Nintendo Switch™ system, and use any of the console''s portable play styles for intense online multiplayer action. Even team up for new 4-player co-op fun in Salmon Run!', 0),
(3, 19.99, 'Splatoon™ 2: Octo Expansion', 'Play as an Octoling in this DLC that features a full-on single-player adventure spanning 80 missions starring Agent 8. Navigate the mysterious underground test facility in a desperate battle to reach the surface of Inkopolis. Escape from the twisted depths, and you''ll be able to join multiplayer battles as an Octoling!', 0),
(3, 59.99, 'Splatoon™ 3', 'Ink, swim, and splat in the freshest shooter around! Enter 4-on-4 ink-slinging battles in this colorful action shooter packed with style and attitude. As a squid-like Inkling, quickly cover your surroundings (and opponents) in ink with wild weaponry and swim through your own color to sneak and splat. Dive into the fresh and fun with family and friends and make waves as a team.', 42),
(3, 24.99, 'Splatoon™ 3: Expansion Pass', 'Splat into the Spire of Order! Take a deeper dive into the expansive world and colorful characters of the Splatoon™ series with a brand-new single-player campaign, Side Order! Step into the role of Agent 8, a young Octoling who defected from the Octarians, see what''s become of Inkopolis Square from Splatoon 2, and make your way up the Spire of Order - where you never quite know what each floor will bring.', 44),
(3, 59.99, 'Super Mario Bros.™ Wonder', 'Welcome to the Flower Kingdom! Mario and his friends have been invited to visit the colorful Flower Kingdom, just a short hop away from the Mushroom Kingdom. Unfortunately, King Bowser has transformed into a flying castle and is causing chaos across their peaceful land. Now our heros must save the day-and the Flower Kingdom-in this wonderous new adventure!', 52),
(3, 59.99, 'Mario Party™ Superstars', 'Join the party and prove you''re the superstar! Roll your dice and race to get the most stars (and sabotage your opponents) on 5 game boards. Each board is filled with treats and tricks. With minigames, star-stealing ghosts, and troublemaking Bowser, you can turn the tables on your friends and family in an instant.', 53),
(3, 59.99, 'Paper Mario™: The Thousand-Year Door', 'Join Mario and friends on an epic paper adventure! A classic story unfolds on the Nintendo Switch system. Collect the Crystal Stars before the bad guys do. The X-Nauts are after the treasure behind the Thousand-Year Door! With a map from Princess Peach-and the help of a few locals-Mario just journey through a colorful world made of paper to find it first.', 42),
(3, 59.99, 'Super Mario Odyssey™', 'Embark on a cap-tivating, globe-trotting adventure! Explore incredibleplaces far from the Mushroom Kingdom as you join Mario and his new ally Cappy on a massive, globe-trotting 3D adventure. Use amaing new abilities-like the power to capture and control objects, animals, and enemies-to collect Power Moons so you can power up the Odyssey airship and save Princess Peach from Bowser''s wedding plans!', 53),
(3, 59.99, 'Super Mario Party™', 'Super-charged fun for friends and family-now with online play in board game mode and minigames! Turn the tables on opponents as you race across the board to collect the most stars in the original 4-player Mario Party series board game mode-now with newly-added online play. Join the full-on frenzy with friends and family!', 21),
(3, 59.99, 'Super Mario™ 3D World + Bowser''s Fury', 'Power up, team up, one up to save the Sprixie Kingdom! Pounce and climb through dozens of colorful courses! Multiply teh fun by teaming up with or competing against friends locally or online to reach each stage''s goal. Explore a seamless feline world in the new Bowser''s Fury adventure! Free-roaming Super Mario gameplay makes a return in this brand-new adventure. Bowser has become gargantuan and lost all control! Team up with Bowser Jr. to explore Lake Lapcat and its islands, complete objectives to collect Cat Shines, and bring his big, bad dad back to normal!', 67),
(3, 59.99, 'Princess Peach™: Showtime!', 'Take the stage as Peach! Help Peach save the Sparkle Theater from the wicked Grape and Sour Bunch, who have set the stage for the ultimate tragedy. Join by Stella, the theater''s guardian, Peach is ready to save the day!', 43),
(3, 44.99, 'Mario Kart™ 8 Duluxe', 'Race with Mario and friends anytime, anywhere! Burn rubber across Mushroom Kingdom raceways-underwater, in teh sky, upside-down in zero-g, and past the finish-for the win! Get revved up for local or online multiplayer, in-game tournaments, a revamped battle mode, and more!', 90),
(3, 24.99, 'Mario Kart™ 8 Duluxe: Booster Course Pass', 'Get an additional game''s worth of courses with the Booster Pass! A total of 48 more courses are racing to the Mario Kart 8 Duluxe game as paid DLC. Highlights include the Yoshi''s Island Course, and returning favorites like DS Waluigi Pinball and Wii Rainbow Road. Whether you''re coasting through teh flowery hills or clinging to the rainbow edges, you''re in for a wild ride!', 98),
(3, 51.99, 'Yoshi''s Crafted World™', 'Get crafty with Yoshi in a handicraft world! Jump into a new Yoshi adventure in a world made of everyday objects-like boxes and paper cups! As Yoshi, you''ll lead up high, gulp down enemies, and set out on a treasure hunt to find all the different collectables. On the flip side, stages can be played backwards, providing new perspectives to explore and new ways to locate some of the more craftily hidden items!', 39),
(3, 39.99, 'Captain Toad™: Treasure Tracker', 'Ready for adventure! Captain Toad in hsi own puzzling quest. Our stubby hero must dodge dangers and track treasures across many trap-filled courses. Survive smoldering volcanoes, hazardous steam engines, haunted houses, and new courses based on the Super Mario Odyssey™ game!', 0),
(3, 5.99, 'Captain Toad™: Treasure Tracker - Special Episode', 'Continue your journey with 18 new challenges, including five brand-new courses!', 0),
(3, 59.99, 'Paper Mario™: The Origami King', 'A new pape-crafted Mario adventure unfolds on Nintendo Switch! The kingdom has been ravaged by an origami menace! Join Mario and his new partner, Olivia, as they battle evil Folded Soldiers, repair the damaged landscape, and try to free Princess Peach''s castle from the clutches of King Olly in this comedy-filled adventure.', 52),
(3, 59.99, 'New Super Mario Bros.™ U Duluxe', 'Two Super Mario Bros. games in one, for double the fun! Join Mario, Luigi, and pals for single or multiplayer fun any time, anywhere! Take on two family-friendly, side-scrolling adventures with up to three friends as you try to save the Mushroom Kingdom. Includes New Super Mario Bros. U and harder, faster New Super Luigi U games-both of which include Nabbit and Toadette as playable characters!', 3),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Legends: Arceus', 'Action meets RPG as the Pokémon series reaches a new frontier. Explore the Hisui  Region - the Sinnoh of old. Build the region''s first Pokédex. Discover newly added types of Pokémon including new regional forms and Noble Pokémon. Players who have data from other select Pokémon games on their Nintendo Switch™ can get in-game bonuses as well.', 89),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Violet', 'Welcome to the wide-open world of the Paldea Region. Catch, battle, and train Pokémon in the Paldea Region, a vast land filled with lakes, towering peaks, wastelands, small towns, and sprawling cities. Explore a wide-open world at your own pace and traverse land, water, and air on a form-shifting Legendary Pokemon-Miraidon. Choose either Sprigatito, Fuecoco, or Quaxly to be your first partner Pokémon before setting of on your journey through Paldea.', 21),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Scarlet', 'Welcome to the wide-open world of the Paldea Region. Catch, battle, and train Pokémon in the Paldea Region, a vast land filled with lakes, towering peaks, wastelands, small towns, and sprawling cities. Explore a wide-open world at your own pace and traverse land, water, and air on a form-shifting Legendary Pokemon-Koraidon. Choose either Sprigatito, Fuecoco, or Quaxly to be your first partner Pokémon before setting of on your journey through Paldea.', 93),
(3, 34.99, 'The Hidden Treasure of Area Zero DLC', 'Continue your Pokemon™ Scarlet and Violet adventure and go beyond the Paldea region with teh Hidden Treasure of Area Zero DLC. In Part 1: The Teal Mask, join a special school trip in the land of Kitakami and learn about the local legend of the Loyal Three Pokemon. In Part 2: The Indigo Disk, study abroad at Blueberry Academy in the Unova region where the curriculum emphasizes Pokémon Battling.', 93),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Brilliant Diamond', 'Catch, train, and battle with your Pokémon on a Journey to try to become the Pokémon League Champion! Welcome to the Sinnoh Region! Rich in nature and with mighty Mount Coronet at its heart, Sinnoh is a land of many myths passed down through teh ages. You''ll choose either Turtwig, Chimchar, or Piplup to be your first partner Pokémon and then set off on your journey to become the Champion of the Pokémon League. Along the way, you''ll run into the mysterious organization Team Galatic, and be able to encounter the legendary Pokémon Dialga', 381),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Shining Pearl', 'Catch, train, and battle with your Pokémon on a Journey to try to become the Pokémon League Champion! Welcome to the Sinnoh Region! Rich in nature and with mighty Mount Coronet at its heart, Sinnoh is a land of many myths passed down through teh ages. You''ll choose either Turtwig, Chimchar, or Piplup to be your first partner Pokémon and then set off on your journey to become the Champion of the Pokémon League. Along the way, you''ll run into the mysterious organization Team Galatic, and be able to encounter the legendary Pokémon Palkia', 302),
(3, 59.99, 'New Pokémon Snap™', 'Explore lush scenery on unknown islands to snap photos of Pokémon in their natural habitats. Seek out and take in-game photographs of Pokémon in their native environments! Snap photos from the NEO-ONE as you encounter and research lively wild Pokémon. You might see unexpected expressions or behaviors - Pokémon patrolling their territory, playing, or lurking in out-of-the-way spots.',43),
(3, 59.99, 'Pokémon™ Sword', 'Get ready for the next Pokémon adventure. A new generation of Pokémon is coming. Begin your adventure as a Pokémon trainer by choosing one of the three new partner Pokémon: Grookey, Scorbunny, or Sobble. Then embark on a journey into the new Galar region, where you''ll challenge the troublemakers Team Yell, hwile unraveling the mystery behind the Legendary Pokémon Zacian and Zamazenta!', 23),
