(6, 1299.00, 'iMac', 'Supercharged by Apple M3 chip. Immersive 24-inch 4.5K Retina display. Strikingly thin all-in-one desktop. Look sharp and sound great with the 1080p FaceTime HD camera, three-mic array, and six-speaker sound system with Spatial Audio. Color-matched Magic Mouse and Magic keyboard included. Available in 7 colors.', 382),
