(6, 249.00, 'Apple Watch Se', 'Call and message even when you don''t have your iPhone nearby with GPS + Cellular models. Get advanced workout metrics and views. Track your sleep stages with the Sleep app, and check your heart rate any time. Innovative safety features including Emergency SOS, Fall Detection, and Crash Detection. Set up any Apple Watch GPS + Cellular model for your kids, even if they don''t have their own iPhone yet. Available in 3 cases finishes.', 329),
