(7, 59.99, 'PS1S Wave Premium Single Monitor Stand', 'Introducing the PS1S Wave Premium Single Monitor Stand – the ultimate in workspace efficiency! It''s the perfect solution for a clutter-free, customizable setup with 180º rotation, top-side installation, integrated cable management, detachable VESA plate, and built-in spring tension. Plus, it comes in 4 cute colors to match your PX248Wave Gaming monitor: Blue, Pink, White, and Black. Upgrade your workspace today!', 382),
(7, 149.99, 'PX248 Wave', 'Designed for FPS gaming, the PX248 Wave is equipped with a FAST IPS panel with a 1ms (GTG) response time equivalent to a 1ms (GTG) TN panel speed.  At 24 inches, 1080p, and a 200Hz refresh rate, elevate the way you game without sacrificing too much. The lightweight, flat, bezel-less design also provides a space-saving solution for all your viewing needs. The PX248 Wave is the ultimate premier IPS gaming monitor that completes your gaming and visual experience without sacrificing quality for performance.', 329),
