(7, 129.99, 'PS2D Dual Monitor Arm Mount', 'PS2D is a dual monitor gas spring mount from Pixio. The perfect accessory to both your Pixio Gaming Monitors. The counterbalance gas-powered spring arm allows for simple height adjustment without the use of tools and is fully adjustable allowing you to set hte monitor to almost any viewing angle. Choose from either the desk clamp or desk grommet option. It also includes an integrated cable management system. PS2D can fit two screens up to 35" in size each, weighing between 2.2 lbs and 30.8 lbs and compatible with either VESA 75x75mm or 100x100mm', 389),
