(9, 14.99, 'Akko Dracula Switch', 'Featuring the POK top case and stem, Akko Dracula switch is designed to be ultra-smooth and comfortable to type on. This marks Akko''s first venture into using POK material, known for its superior water and impact resistence compared to POM. While POK may slightly change color over time, we''ve thoughtfully chosen black adn dark red shades to enhance durability and aesthetics. Aditionally, POK is considered to have the potential to be a more sustainable material than POM. The stem also features an additional hole at the bottom to improve airflow and enhance smoothness. 5-pin and fits keycaps with standard MX structure. 45 pcs in a pack.', 32), 
(9, 13.99, 'Akko Botany Switch', 'Akko Botany is a mid-pitched version of Rosewood with a clear bottom-out sound profile. The color of the switch is inspired by "Haworthia cooperi" in a light bluish green pattern. The switch features our custom Nylon (Pro) stem, a PA12 blend top cover, and a PA6 bottom housing, creating a unique material combination. 5-pin and fits keycaps with standard MS structure.', 281), 
